Communication Policies:
•	Slack channel is primary communication source
•	Use @[name] for immediate replies
•	@channel should be used for questions or statements that apply to everyone within the channel
•	Questions can be answered by anyone on the team, regardless of their role

Meeting Policies:
•	Weekly meetings at 5:30 on Monday
  o	Location/format can be established on a week-by-week basis
  o	Agenda, location, format to be laid out and communicated to team by end of day Sunday
